description: Erection of a part 8, part 7 part 6 storey building on the eastern part of the site around the EDF substation facing Skerne Road for a 150 bedroom hotel (with conference/banqueting & meeting facilities) and 137 flats. Erection of a part 16, part 11, part 6 storey building comprising 222 flats, on the western part of the site (the Riverside).
